ZH:凡人都有自己的优点和缺点。
EN: Everyone has their own strengths and weaknesses.

ZH:凡是有耳朵的动物都可以听到声音。
EN: All animals with ears can hear sounds.

ZH:凡是下雨的时候，他总是忘记带伞。
EN: Whenever it rains, he always forgets to bring an umbrella.

ZH:凡是通过考试的学生都可以得到证书。
EN: Students who pass the exam can receive a certificate.

ZH:凡是加入俱乐部的人都会受到特别的关照。
EN: Those who join the club will receive special attention.

ZH:凡是不服从规则的员工都会受到相应的惩罚。
EN: Employees who do not follow the rules will face appropriate punishment.

ZH:凡是有爱心的人都会受到他人的尊重。
EN: Those who are compassionate will be respected by others.

ZH:凡是有毅力的人都能够取得成功。
EN: People with determination can achieve success.

ZH:凡是用心工作的人都会得到回报。
EN: Those who work hard will be rewarded.

ZH:凡是有勇气追求梦想的人都会实现目标。
EN: People who have the courage to pursue their dreams will achieve their goals.

ZH:凡是遵守规则的人都不会受到处罚。
EN: Those who abide by the rules will not be punished.

ZH:凡是犯错的人都必须承担责任。
EN: People who make mistakes must take responsibility.

ZH:凡是明白真相的人都不会被欺骗。
EN: Those who understand the truth will not be deceived.

ZH:凡是有责任感的人都会尽心尽力。
EN: People with a sense of responsibility will do their best.

ZH:凡是努力学习的学生都能取得好成绩。
EN: Students who study hard can achieve good grades.

ZH:凡是诚实的人都会受到信任。
EN: Honest people will be trusted.

ZH:凡是经过培训的员工都能胜任工作。
EN: Employees who have received training can handle their jobs.

ZH:凡是准时到达的人都会受到赞扬。
EN: People who arrive on time will be praised.

ZH:凡是有梦想的人都会为之奋斗。
EN: Those who have dreams will strive for them.

ZH:凡是改变自己的人生的人都会经历困难。
EN: People who change their lives will experience challenges.
